! write_fits_fts

! PURPOSE

! Write the FTS spectra in a file to a fits table

! SYNTAX

! @ write_fits_fts input_file output_file

! tell CLASS to be quiet
sic MESSAGE CLASS S=FE

set angle sec

say Converting &1 to fits file &2

file in &1

find /telescope 30M-F0*

! A) set rest frequency to 12CO(2-1)
! B) smooth FTS to 2.54km/s channels
! @herapipe/class/loop_write.class 230538.000

! sys "rm &2"
fits write &2 /mode index /bits -32

